Dilys Watling https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dilys_Watling 0 Dilys Watling (born as Dilys Rhys Jones, 5 May 1943 in Fulmer Chase, Buckinghamshire) is an English actress, best known for appearing on British television (Coronation Street, The Benny Hill Show and The Two Ronnies).
